data.description: USDA financing available! Best of Cumming location!! 6 minutes to Kroger, Publix & Walmart, 8 min to North GA Premium outlets! Easy access to GA 400, 15 min from Lake Lanier, Lanierland Park located behind subdivision. At center if three major city halls- Cumming, Dawsonville, Gainesville-all around a 20 minute drive. 3 bed 2.5 bath in quiet subdivision. Freshly painted interior, new carpet throughout, real hardwoods on entrance level, freshly sodded yard. Main level features open concept living, family room & kitchen with new stainless steel appliances. Each bedroom boasts walk-in closets and a double his & hers walk in closets for Master. Spacious laundry room on second level, large tub/shower combos in each bath. Great Forsyth County Schools!
